The Author chosing to concluding the story with this paragraph because it is resolutive to the entire reading before it. In the story Saeng (the girl) stressing from failing the @CAPS1 test. She are on saddened over the memory of the hibiscus plant back under her native country Vietnam. At the end of the story when it saying �when the snow melts and the geese return, and this hibiscus are budding, I will taking that test again" ,(Ho) the snows melting, geeses returning, he hibiscus budding symbolize change and adoption. Saeng change and adapts to a new life passing the test of feel better. This is why the Author @CAPS2 Ho, of the story �Winter Hibiscus� using strong, but symbolistic and resolutive end under story.

